{
  "stem": "676.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You, you, you have to go and do something, you know, to get away from there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they got out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, they were caught, also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- we were all taken to Sered, which was, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which was-- what was it?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like a-- [NON-ENGLISH] they called it-- which is like a place where they brought everybody together and from which the trains went.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like a transit station?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were all separated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was in one, one place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- I was with my brother in another place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All in Sered, but not in the same bunks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They separated us, though.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All in different barracks in the same place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was just where they processed everybody into the trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while we-- oh, I still want to tell the story about Sered when we were in Nove Mesto nad Vahom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They, they took us into-- they put us into a place which was-- I believe it must have been like a retirement home or a-- you know, for elderly people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there they put everybody there before they took us to Sered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a-- I was there with my little brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had an aunt there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she has, she had two daughters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found out that she said that during the night, there is one piece in the barbed wire there that is cut.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she's going to try to escape with her two daughters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I begged her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, please, [NON-ENGLISH], don't leave us here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Please take us with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she promised, children, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wouldn't leave you behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm going to take you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the next morning we got up and she was gone with the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
